high_descs: Turn around to your right move forward then turn left, head to the coffee maker
Pick up the mug in front of the coffee maker on the counter
Turn to your left head to the microwave above the stove
Open the microwave then put in and out the mug then close the microwave
Turn to your right and head to the coffee maker
Put the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the warm mug on the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn around, move forward, then turn left, to approach the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug on the counter, in front of the coffee maker.
Turn left, go straight, then turn right at the stove and look up at the microwave.
Heat the mug inside of the microwave.
Turn right, go forward, then turn left to face the coffee maker.
Put the mug at the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug at the coffee maker.

high_descs: Go right and stand in front of the coffee maker.
Pick the white mug up from the counter.
Turn left and then right to face the stove.
Put the mug into the microwave and turn it on and then off and open the door to get the mug out and shut the door.
Go to the right to stand in front of the coffee maker.
Put the mug under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed mug under a coffee maker.
